data.description: Close-in North Creek Short Plat on One Acre has Preliminary Approval and is waiting for your finishing touch! Ready to build 8 units this year, plus an existing home (9 Doors!)! Existing home has 2nd primary bedroom on main floor with triple closets! Potential to change Duplex into 4-plex lots per engineering. Easy build with open space area fpr set-up/trucks. Fully fenced, large area for extra parking spot, sports courts, etc. Wood from existing detached garage can be reclaimed. Future zoning changes may result in additional development potential, buyer to verify. Sought-after Northshore School District. Minutes to Mill Creek Town Center, Canyon Park, restaurants/shopping/parks via Hwy 527 and I-405/I-5 for commuting.
